Author: cerareece
Text: Omg I know its like my rational brain shuts off. I wanted to be like girl you don't know how strong and mean I actually am but then was like "did you imply I am small and delicate that's all I'm gonna take from this conversation"

Author: tenderistloin
Text: I do jiu jitsu and whenever someone says “but you’re tiny, a big dude could still crush you,” I have a moment of “FUCK YOU IM A STONE-COLD KILLAH” which morphs into “oh my, I’m actually sincerely happy you just told me I could be killed because I’m tiny.”  It’s confusing.
